    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Island Dwellers》是一款回合制策略游戏，你将带领部落应对海平面上升的挑战。为族人分配任务、解锁科技、建造繁荣村落，并在航行到不同气候地区寻找更美好未来的过程中不断适应新环境。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023960/extras/35d1bd681401de4f784b08a32e540762.avif?t=1755616144\" width=614 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023960/extras/392c00e162e5cdf63581b5db562fb236.poster.avif?t=1755616144\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023960/extras/392c00e162e5cdf63581b5db562fb236.webm?t=1755616144\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023960/extras/392c00e162e5cdf63581b5db562fb236.mp4?t=1755616144\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>随着时间的推移，你的岛屿将逐渐被海水侵蚀。平衡你的人们当前的需求与逃离正在下沉的岛屿的必要性。制定一个策略，以确保你的部落在不断上涨的潮水和缩小的土地中生存下去。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023960/extras/381af8d10a6fd66003800dcecbb16b3d.avif?t=1755616144\" width=614 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023960/extras/cf74553381d37a496b508e5e71ea2c8e.poster.avif?t=1755616144\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023960/extras/cf74553381d37a496b508e5e71ea2c8e.webm?t=1755616144\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023960/extras/cf74553381d37a496b508e5e71ea2c8e.mp4?t=1755616144\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>分配任务给你的人民，小心管理有限的资源，建立一个繁荣的定居点。教育部落的孩子们，以确保未来世代有一个强大的社区。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023960/extras/361c6a682cf3b954bc0a6a9685e8beda.avif?t=1755616144\" width=614 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023960/extras/8bb6aff969b949ed018fb0226b96e36b.poster.avif?t=1755616144\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023960/extras/8bb6aff969b949ed018fb0226b96e36b.webm?t=1755616144\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023960/extras/8bb6aff969b949ed018fb0226b96e36b.mp4?t=1755616144\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>通过建造一座雄伟的神庙、找回所有失落的遗物，或解锁隐藏的知识来让神灵刮目相看，甚至推翻他们。无论你选择哪条道路，你的部落命运都掌握在你手中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023960/extras/5fb5a04e13a7662a382eb2c0ef99f432.avif?t=1755616144\" width=614 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023960/extras/ac54d7ed8ba076e8f73a75438430b194.poster.avif?t=1755616144\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023960/extras/ac54d7ed8ba076e8f73a75438430b194.webm?t=1755616144\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023960/extras/ac54d7ed8ba076e8f73a75438430b194.mp4?t=1755616144\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>当你的部落离开祖居之地时，他们必须适应新的环境。每种独特的气候都有其自身的挑战和机遇。学习并适应每个岛屿的新条件，带领你的部落走向胜利。</p>",
